{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Horror metroid<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727520/extras/ForSteam3.gif?t=1733243699\" />Survival horror with elements of metroidvania.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A dark, atmospheric adventure in the surroundings of retrofutristic Sci-Fi from a solo developer. The main character finds himself on an abandoned colonization ship Calypso, drifting somewhere in space. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727520/extras/ForSteam1.gif?t=1733243699\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And now a person who does not have any special knowledge must be able to survive and get off this ship. Everything is complicated by a mysterious creature, a kind of creature, which made the ship look like an abandoned one. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727520/extras/ForSteam6.gif?t=1733243699\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It will hunt the main character, and he will be forced to run away, hide, scare away and cheat in order not to get caught in his hot embrace. And it also turns out that the crew of the ship is not completely dead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727520/extras/ForSteam8.gif?t=1733243699\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will have to solve puzzles, find keys, craft various devices, shoot back at local residents who will be glad of any mistake you make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727520/extras/ForSteam7.gif?t=1733243699\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2727520/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733243699","background_raw":"https://shared.aka